714419f-a.title: Manhattan: 74th Street (East) - 2nd Avenue
714419f-a.text:
East 74th Street, north side, west from but not including Second Ave.
Shown under demolition is a row of 4-story tenements (Nos. 239 west to
225 inclusive). The 4-story building shown in the foreground and adjoining
the demolition is No. 253 and is just west of Second Ave. The 2-story
affair (No. 257) is at the rear of the corner building, No. 1421 Second Ave.
December 28, 1936.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
